title: No VODS on the VODS page -.-
body: Wanting to watch the NA CS I went to the VODS page. Here you find the matches and where the VODS are suppose to be. You click it and it just tell you the VODS are not yet available. Just delete the page if your not going to keep it up to date.

replies.body: Straaaaange. I've got the page pulled up now and I'm seeing 2 matches from Week 5 and 10 matches from Week 4. Make sure that you're checking [**this page**](http://www.lolesports.com/en_US/vods/na-lcs/na_2017_summer), and if it's still not showing up trying [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)
Hmm still not working for me.  The LCS VODS are there and working the NA Challenger are not

Weeeeiiiiiiird.....I can still see those Challenger vods on my end. Make sure you refreshed those [**cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), and maybe try opening that page in a different browser or private/incognito mode? Let me know if either of those work.
